Hi Riot! I wanna ask if I can purchase the icon without getting the border?
I really like the Kiko icon but i saw the icon could only be purchase in a bundle. None of my friends purchase the bundle so it would look super silly if I am the only star guardian with a border. But i really like the icon...
Will the icon be sold separately? If no... bye bye Kiko! {{item:3070}} {{sticker:cass-cry}}
